    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been fully overhauled. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is impeccable, with a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing OEM Sachs components. The factory paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its original Nappa leather integrity with no bolster wear. Mechanically synchronized and aesthetically flawless, this E46 represents the zenith of naturally aspirated M-performance.",
