      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2012 BMW M3 Coupe in Alpine White over Fox Red Novillo leather. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since new. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero chips, swirls, or imperfections, while the carbon fiber roof remains flawless. Inside, the leather is supple and matte, showing no signs of wear or bolster compression, and the cabin still carries that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect; a comprehensive service history accompanies the car, including recent preventive rod bearing replacement and throttle body actuators. Every button, switch, and feature operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example of the legendary S65 V8 engine.",
